name: Vessels Less Traveled
description: Welcome to the Circulatory System company. Thank you for accepting the Specialist position of the Upper Limb. You're the perfect addition to our team, and we know you'll accomplish great things here. We begin our training at the Ascending Aorta. On the way, you’ll meet friendly people who will give you important information. Draw closer to them to start a conversation. Make sure to interact on all available resources. Most of all, don’t forget to have fun!
